# No testing files (Pulse UI)

**Do not add test files** (e.g. `*.test.tsx`, `*.spec.ts`, `__tests__/`) to this repo. Testing is handled separately. If the user asks for tests, suggest they be added in the external test suite or pipeline, not in pulse-ui.
